OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FBaxter the camel has joined protestors
OL,7,Foutside the Shire Hall in Warwick
OL,8,Fdemonstrating against plans which
OL,9,Fcould see beds removed from a
OL,10,Fcommunity hospital in Shipston-on-
OL,11,FStour for good.
OL,13,FThe Ellen Badger Hospital has been
OL,14,Fwithout beds since 2022, a temporary
OL,15,Fremoval, which could be made permanent
OL,16,Fas part of plans currently under
OL,17,Fconsultation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
