OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FProtesters wanted to share their
OL,7,Fanger, explaining 'a hospital without
OL,8,Fbeds is like a camel without a hump',
OL,9,Fahead of the Warwickshire County
OL,10,FCouncil Adult Health Overview &
OL,11,FCommittee meeting on Wednesday 22
OL,12,FJanuary.
OL,14,FThe two options under consultation are
OL,15,Ffor 35 beds to be distributed across
OL,16,Fthe Ellen Badger Hospital, Leamington
OL,17,FSpa Hospital, and Stratford Hospital.
OL,18,FIt would reduce the number of beds
OL,19,Fcurrently at Stratford Hospital and
OL,20,FLeamington Spa Hospital and return up
OL,21,Fto 12 beds to the Ellen Badger site.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
