OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FThe other option is to provide all 35
OL,7,Fbeds to the Leamington Spa Hospital
OL,8,Fand Stratford Hospital, leaving the
OL,9,FEllen Badger Hospital without any beds.
OL,11,FOn its website, NHS Coventry and
OL,12,FWarwickshire Integrated Care Board
OL,13,Fsaid: "We know patients recover better
OL,14,Fand more quickly at home.
OL,16,F"We have services in place to support
OL,17,Fthat and it means more people than
OL,18,Fever are able to leave our acute
OL,19,Fhospitals and go straight back to
OL,20,Ftheir homes or usual place of
OL,21,Fresidences.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
