OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,F"However, there will always be people
OL,7,Fwho need further rehabilitation
OL,8,Fsupport as an inpatient in a community
OL,9,Fhospital before they are able to go
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,F"In South Warwickshire, we have 35
OL,13,Fcommunity rehabilitation beds
OL,14,Favailable to support this cohort of
OL,15,Fpeople and we support about 550
OL,16,Fpatients a year through this service."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
