OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,F"This consultation seeks to understand
OL,7,Fthe potential impacts of the proposed
OL,8,Fchanges to the location of our 35
OL,9,Frehabilitation beds in South
OL,10,FWarwickshire and gather feedback
OL,11,Fbefore any decisions are made."
OL,13,FAlasdair Elliott, Chairman of the Beds
OL,14,Ffor Badger campaign was at the protest
OL,15,Fand said the hospital "means an awful
OL,16,Flot to the local people" and stressed
OL,17,Fthe the importance of returning the
OL,18,Fcommunity care beds to the hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
