OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FHe said the removal of the beds is
OL,7,F"the straw that broke the camel's
OL,8,Fback" adding: "The beds are very
OL,9,Fneeded... if nothing changes, the
OL,10,Frural community in South Warwickshire
OL,11,Fis going to be left in the dark.
OL,13,F"We're going to keep fighting. What we
OL,14,Freally want to do is get around the
OL,15,Ftable and have a mature conversation
OL,16,Fabout what's going on.
OL,18,F"Shipston is a community and we need a
OL,19,Fcommunity hospital."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
