OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FJoining him at the protest was Rebecca
OL,7,FFosset from Joseph's Amazing Camels, a
OL,8,Fbusiness in Idlicote near Shipston.
OL,9,FShe says it was important to bring
OL,10,Ftheir camel Baxter to the protest to
OL,11,Fhelp the fight.
OL,13,FShe explained: "We live locally to the
OL,14,FEllen Badger and it's very important
OL,15,Fto us that there are beds in the
OL,16,Fhospital. I think Shipston's got the
OL,17,Fhump, you can't have a camel without a
OL,18,Fhump or a hospital without beds."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
