OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FSharon Bygate who lives near the
OL,7,Fhospital says it was vital for her and
OL,8,Fher children when husband was being
OL,9,Fcared for before he passed away in
OL,10,F2014 at the age of 46.
OL,12,FAndrew Bygate was diagnosed with a
OL,13,Fglioblastoma multiform brain tumour in
OL,14,FSeptember 2006. At the time, Andrew
OL,15,Fand Sharon's third child was just a
OL,16,Fweek old.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
