OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FOver the course of eight years, Andrew
OL,7,Fhad three operations on his brain. He
OL,8,Fdied in October 2014, eight years
OL,9,Fafter doctors gave him just two years
OL,10,Fto live.
OL,12,FSharon says being able to have nurses
OL,13,Fcare for Andrew just around the corner
OL,14,Ffrom their house at the Ellen Badger
OL,15,FHospital made it possible for their
OL,16,Fchildren, then aged 12, 10 and 8 to
OL,17,Fvisit him regularly during his final
OL,18,Fweeks.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
