OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F375A1737653789
OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,F"What Shipston allowed was for my
OL,7,Fchildren to pop in after school after
OL,8,Ftheir clubs, before school sometimes,
OL,9,Fand they could just go and see him.
OL,11,F"Andrew nearly died twice before he
OL,12,Factually did, and I had to make a last
OL,13,Fminute dash, and I just couldn't have
OL,14,Fdone that if he was in Warwick.
OL,16,F"For my children to have that precious
OL,17,Ftime with their dad - we will always
OL,18,Fremember it. We were with him day and
OL,19,Fnight, he was never on his own."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
