OL,3,C'Shipston's got the hump' as camel
OL,4,Cjoins protest over hospital beds
OL,6,FShe said without the option of a bed
OL,7,Fnearby, it would have been
OL,8,F"exhausting", she said: "It would have
OL,9,Fbeen so difficult. It's exhausting
OL,10,Fhaving someone dying anyway, the whole
OL,11,Fprocess is awful, you are trying to
OL,12,Fdeal with your children who can see
OL,13,Ftheir dad is dying. To have it there
OL,14,Fwas so important to me."
OL,16,FThe public consultation period runs
OL,17,Funtil 14 February.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/11
